yea..to anyone reading this.. if someone says that.. u might not want to trust them.. they will lie..unless they are a better person than this individual.. im so pissed.. i hate it.. she lied right to my face.. i mean seriously..i obviously trust the other person more.. they told the truth.. u lied.. u lie to my face whenever i ask about it.. im not that mad that u said something.. but dont lie about it.. that hurts worse than anything..i learned my lesson with you.. i just wish i could have before i told u that..u probably told everyone by now..would be mad if u were me? y did u ask my sister.. a million times i told u.. i HATE her.. like she would know anything about me anyway..wat if i decided to lie to you.. look u in the eye and deny everything..y do ppl do that..

im so pissed of right now.. i hate everyone in my family.. i want to leave but i have no where to go.. i have no one to turn to.. my mom favors my sister because nobody can stand it when she throws her fits..so this is what happened.. i had an extra half hr online b/c my mom messed up when she was doin something to the parental controls.. b/c i had that 1/2 hr my sister decided she wanted to go online.. so i let her..the computer signed her off immediately.. she flipped out.. tried to beat the crap out of me n was hitting all the walls n crap like that.. n wen i went back on she pulled the plug out of the wall. n then my mom came home and changed the time so that i only had until 9 all week.. my sister however had until 930 on weeknights and 10 on weekends.. so all week i asked her to change it..but of course she wouldnt.. cuz im not my sister n i dont throw fits to get my way.. so i yelled at my mom today.. after a whole week of even more limited access on the computer.. n i tried to sign on her name to change her password and everything.. so i told her that i was one step away from changing her password so she came out and screamed her head off at me.. like always.. my sister would get away with anything but if i do it i get in trouble.. n since i rarely do anything bad she brings up stuff from like weeks ago and even crap from last year.. she told me i was a bad kid who needed all these restrictions online b/c i stole frome the mall (once and only once about a month ago i guess) and she yelled at me for skipping class.. which i did once last year.. n she yelled at me for being friends with people who want to die their hair n get piercings.. yea.. cuz any of that crap matters..so she cam right up to my face n hit me a couple of times and screamed for like an hour in my face about absolutely nothing..ppl wonder why i can barely hear them..mentally unstable people scream in my ears for no reason..i hate my family so much.. last night at the award ceremony my mom insisted on coming.. i told her i didnt want her there n that parents were not allowed but she had to come anyway.. i hate her so much.. my family is embarassing.. im 15 i dont need them to be by my side anymore.. i really dont want them there either.. this week has been so bad.. the only good day was monday..n i know why.. but tuesday wasnt so great n neither was weds, thurs, and today..of course all this crap has to happen wen me and someone who means a lot to me are kinda having a fight.. one day they were mad at me n now im mad at them.. it sucks but life goes on.. its kinda good in a way.. im realizing that they arent so important to me.. they betrayed me n i dont really need someone like that in my life.. they still mean so much but.. its just gunna b different now.. i wont NEED to be next to them all the time.. i need my space.. n i think they do too..idk.. im really pissed right now i was thinking before about leaving but i was like where can i go and spend the night w.o telling my mom or anything.. heathers?.. no.. shes in boston.. stacy?.. no shes goin to florida.. i couldnt even go to my dads cuz he went to see his father.. n i dont really know fays family to well so i dont wanna put them out.. so i was outta options.. so i got stuck here in this hell hole with the people i hate..

i need to drive n get away from them!!!

Living in a Dream

What if we lived only in our dreams?
Everything would always be good,
Just live how you want and do what you please
This world will finally be as it should.

No pain will you feel,
No tears will you shed;
The world is as you want it,
As you lie peacefully in bed.

Everyone will be who you need,
You don't need to search for that one;
Think of the person you want,
Then no more troubles.. just fun. 

No such thing as bad news,
No reasons to cry,
Only happiness and laughter,
Never the thought of suicide.

The fear of death never crosses,
The love you share never dies.
The one you need is always right there
Never saying those painful goodbyes. 

You create your own world,
And decide what others do.
No broken hearts and feelings
'Cuz they won't ever hurt you.

Never feelin like the outcast,
All alone in this state,
Friends surround your every side,
Making sure your day was great.

Hiden from the outside world,
Where everything is sad,
Hopes and dreams are always broken,
All situations turn out bad.

ok.. so.. i thought i trusted someone a lot.. i told them something that i only told one other person.. i told them not to say anything and they knew it was hard for me to tell them..and i cried after it and was sick to my stomach for days about telling them..then i thought they forgot about it so i was ok.. i guess it really didnt matter to much and yea... no.. they remembered.. and after all that i went through they decided it was ok to tell someone.. so today a friend approaches me and says wat i told that 1st person.. shes like yea.. they said this to me n i thought we should talk about it.. i dont mind that she knows.. but y wouldnt they ask first..they told her everything.. i mean seriously.. i had to explain a lot..

Why trust people??

we need to talk this out.. if they told someone else then i'll flip..


actually im kinda happy they told her..it means i didnt.. n i love my friend a lot.. ive tried to tell her this but it didnt work..shes the ONLY one it would b ok with me to tell about it.. mayb she knew that??... wow.. i dont even no anymore..

ok.. i really messed up thursday.. well.. i didnt.. i wanted to say this for a while.. idk wat i was thinking..i could lose them over this..i could be miserable for a long time about this..i almost cried and puked in everyone of my classes.. except gym.. i did cry.. friday i was thinkin about wat i did then it would go away n  i jus didnt care anymore.. it was over.. kinda.. idk if it'll be brought up again.. but its a risk i have to take. everytime i see this person i get completely sick feeling.. my heart even stops..i was at the mall last night and even though they were all i thought about wen i saw them i started the randomest conversation so that i could make it look like i was deep in conversation so we wouldnt have to talk..it didnt work.. i didnt stick to my plan.. idc.. it wasnt as bad as i had imagined..heather bought a coffee.. hehe n the non coffee drinker that is myself drank almost half the cup while she was in the potty.. then idk.. but the soda machine 8 heather 2 dollars when she tried to get change for marilyn..me n heather were waiting for marilyn to come so we rode the escaltor up and down for about half an hour or so.. it was fun.. we saw a sign that said no sneakers or wheeled things on escalator.. so i was stumped.. how do u go down then? we went down w/ r sneakers anyway.. I GOT A GREEN BELT .. n its the beautifulest thing ever.. this whole thing is scaring me.. idk wat to think.. n everytime i think about it i get sad.. i want something to happen but i dont want things to never b the same.. i'd die if that happened.. even though i dont mean as much as they do to me i still feel i need them.. how would i go through life w/o them now that i met them..well.. this is def. a thing to write a poem about.. so i think thats wat im gunna do.. if i get it done i'll post it.. or u may just c it as an awaymessage..cuz i want them to see it too..idk.. i feel a lil broken n lost right now.. y do people do this??

i really hate EVERYONE right now.. execpt marilyn n heather.. who i love..o n ryan n the other ppl i didnt really talk to..idk.. i just want to hurt everyone b/c i hate em all right about now.. 
o n wat happened today.. nothing.. couldnt really eat again either.. but im trying cuz puff n cheryl said i had to..



i dont wanna hate everyone.. but right now i do..i think i need sleep n a good malling journey with heather n mer..

i cant believe i did what i did today.. it was so stupid too. the second it happened i felt like i was gunna throw up every where and never stop.  i still feel that way..it sucks..why did i have to have that dream? and why did i have to share it? and why did i have to explain it... i feel so sick..i think im gunna puke..

in lab today i was practically dead.. i looked like i was hung over or sumthin.. i couldn't move n i couldn't talk.. it was weird..i was too tired.. it sucks b/c i stayed up until like 11 to read lord of the flies and only got to  where we were supposed to be on like wednesday or sumthin.. so during break me n kristal went for our walk around the school and it kinda woke me up. so then i went to math n me n veronica left for like 20mins n did laps around the school.. then i went to rotc n almost cried.. i hate it so much.. i just realized it today.. wen im overly tired i get so0o0 emotional.. i'll cry for nothing. like in rotc i almost cried n i wasnt even thinking about anything..so then i started thinking about the other time i was all crazy with emotions b/c i was tired.. n it kinda mad me happy.. but who cares.. i went to lunch. n forgot my essay in my locker for english. then went to give it to her in history. we have a test tomorro.. i think i may just pass this one..n then spanish.. i dont even no wats goin on in that class.. i never pay attention.. but i still get straigh 100's

i dont know whats goin on..im so mad n sad n all that crap.. i dont wanna b depressed and crap anymore.. it gets annoying to other people so i try to be as happy as i can..everything really sucks. i cant stand it. i just want it to be back to normal. i want stacy to be better, i wanna talk about how i feel, i dont want to feel alone or scared anymore, n i dont want kristal to leave. i hate this year so much. i started off hating it but then it was ok now i hate it again. i got used to everything in the first semester. i really liked it.. but now its changed n i hate it.. i dont want stacy to be sick. shes like my little sister. shes so sick she had to go to the hospital..she has to get better.. i miss her..i wish i could be sick for her. eventhough with my immune system or w/e it'd prolly kill me.. i want to be able to go up to people and tell them wats on my mind..i really mean this towards danielle..i wanna jus tell her that im afraid to really talk to her or im her and everything like that. im so afraid that she'll be mean to me and yell at me n call me annoying again. i dont want her to n i feel that if i keep being distant from her she cant do that b/c there is nothing to say it against..but i miss talkin to her. i think shes a lot of fun to be around. i feel so alone.. its not even funny..idk y..i feel like some many people i really care about dont care about me. i care about my friends more than i care about myself. i wish they could understand that..i hate that i dont mean that much to them.. i hate high school sometimes just b/c of the way i can b friends with someone but then once were outta class they r with their other friends n im alone.. thats y i get scared about like grade level assemblys n crap.. but w/e i dont care.. hs will b over soon n the people who really care will still b with me.. i hate being scared.. im always afraid of bein alone or missin the bus or jus other stupid BS like that.. i dont want kristal to leave.. sometimes we fight n she yells n i get mad but its over in like a min. she always makes me laugh..even if its just for a second..just a random BAM! from her makes me laugh.. or a talk about bams.. i'll miss that for the week or 2.. 
 we took a stress test in english.. wat fun.. we r no where near being done we got threw like 5-10 slides n i already have over 300.. i think im a lil stressed.. n i didnt even include the whole divorce n re-married thing cuz i wasnt sure about it.. that would b at least another hundred...plus the whole hell that was this week.. idk anymore.. life really sucks..

wow..im so sick of all this drama.. i really hate people sometimes..y me?.. y do people have to take things out on me... i accept it from a few but others no!! jus stop.. mayb someday u can attain the respect of being able to BS on me but not yet.. thats something thats earned.. y do people take things out on me... like i control wat happens... keep it to urself.. n dont make me feel like crap jus b/c ur in a bad mood.. i get like that too.. i dont take it out on u so dont do it to me.. i'll be there if u wanna talk about.. i'll listen n try to stop if its about me.. but if it has nothing to do with me dont take it out on me.. jus b/c i try to hide all my crap to myself doesnt mean i feel no pain n u can start to make me feel miserable..im sick of it.. people have to learn.. im not talkin to the one who made me miserable today.. give it a week n if im still pissed its over.. i wont like it n u prolly wont either but it has to be done.. i cant take it... wat if it happens again.. wat do u want me to do then..i cant stand it..i tried to make u feel better n i showed u i cared.. wat did u do... u bitched it all out on me.. I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING!!


i didnt hurt anyone, so y m i being screwed over ... AGAIN...

i rememeber i was actualy gunna update on here b/c i never do. i only have this one part this.. idk wat to call it. w/e .. i realized i have anger issues..i get made at supid things. n it carries on for a long time... if something happens in like 4th period i jus keep gettin madder n madder until i go to bed. n then sometimes i wake up mad like that.. people really get me mad..if u didnt guess im goin to bed mad tonight.. im gunna update like two more times to see if i can veiw my journal... if i can then i dont need a new 1.. that would make things better...

this really sucks i was waitin for my journal to reach the one year old mark but no.. i cant even veiw it anymore.. after every entry its blocked b/c of parental controls.. i'll prolly make a new one or sumthin.. i'll post it here for a while until i get everything i want from this one...wat an amazin way to end such a sucky day!!! people really suck sometimes!

Well, I tried to do this last night but it didn't work because I clicked the thing the wrong way and it closed itself somehow. It didn't save anything from the entry. I remember I was going to talk about my sucky week. I know that because i don't even remember Monday i didn't mention anything about it. I kinda remember some stuff about Tuesday. It was Multicultural Food Day in ROTC. I had a wonton from Emilyn. It was really good but i almost puked it up everywhere because I've been sick. Thats all i had at the whole food day thing. Then i finished the day and stayed after to talk to lea. It never happened. It was supposed to. I waited while she took a test. Roni, Jess!!!, and I were just hanging at Roni's locker. I missed Jess so much last year. She left over Christmas vacation and never came back, until this year. So they gave up and left and i waited. I told them to give me like five minutes and if i wasn't doin anything I'd meet them at the library. I was at my locker and i saw lea so i was walking with her for a little while. I asked her if she was done but i don't think i ever got an answer so i thought that was where she was going.  I was right behind her but then i looked down and she was gone so i thought she went to finish her test or something. I went for a walk because i told her to call me when she was ready. I met up with Roni and Jess and we went to the library. They were going crazy because they needed to smoke their cigarettes. Then we were talking about all the stuff Jess did and it suprised me because i thought she was such a good girl. She seemed like an angel last year when we would always hang out in the morning and in gym. Roni started talking about how Jess has done so much crap. She gets drunk every now and then. That really didn't suprise me because i know losts of people around my age who get drunk. Then she said how Jess has smoked weed and used ectasy. So then they were having their own little conversation and i was just staring at the school. I saw lea leave so i called her. Of course, she didn't answer. Someone else did and they were lieing to me about who they were with and everything. As if i didn't see them walking to the deli together. So we went back to the school and i was in the road screaming the worst word i knew at them. Of course, Jess was being all angelic and said she really hated that word, but i had to do it again because i was that pissed. Then all of Roni and Jess' friends were hanging out in the hallway so i stayed with them.  Then Andrew walked by so i stayed with him. I knew that he was on my bus because i have known him since like seventh grade and i used to walk to his house because he lives by Mike, Heather, and Ryan. So we were standing there at the West platform and i went around to say hi to everyone i knew. At this point lea decides to call. I don't even know why because i ignored each phone call in fear i would say or do something i would regret. I got on the bus, went home, and managed my anger. 

Wednesday. Well, I remembered on the bus i got hit with a wave of really bad depression. I almost started crying in ROTC but i got the tears to go back in and was able to blame the water-y-ness on a long powerful yawn. So then i went to lunch and needed to talk to Marilyn. So, luckily, Stacy had "some business to attend to" during lunch. I took Marilyn out of the lunch room but there were too many people in the hallway for my liking. So we went to the bathroom and went into a stall because there were to many people in there too.  I showed her; I had been crying the whole way to the bathroom because the whole situation depressed me and I couldn't hold it in any longer. When Marilyn figured it out she almost cried too. We just stayed there for a while, as she was holding me in comfort, until the eye-puffiness went down. Then we went back to lunch. I went to the rest of my classes just like any ordinary day. Then i stayed after because the whole day i was asking lea to stay after. All she sed was "idk" so i thought she was going to. At the end of the day i was at my locker with Kristal and Stacy. Then Kristal left because she wasn't going to stay after. She came back just as lea walked by and said she wasn't going to stay after. Then Stacy left and so did Kristal. I was just with Marilyn and i told her i would walk her to detention. Then i saw Kristal again and she stayed for a little while to take a test. I was on the phone with lea for a while trying to work this crap out. It was going okay but then i saw Marilyn walk over to me and she didn't look right. I wasn't sure at first but then her eyes got really red. I told lea i had to go and i think i sounded mad and i wanted to apologize and explain that i had to help Marilyn with this because she helped me a little earlier that day. Then we went to get some food from Stacy's locker but it was bad. It must have been at least two days old. It was so gross. Then Marilyn left because her mom picked her up. So again i was alone. I called Roni and she was coming to the school to get her books so i was with her for the little while. Then she got her friend to drive her home. Again i was alone. I went back to school and got my books. Then i waited for the bus and Failynn ditched me for JD... GEEEEZZEE!!! Then i had a panic attack because i thought i missed the bus. I would have been stuck there until five if i missed the bus. Good thing i didn't! It's just always the last bus there i guess. I forgot to mention another thing about Marilyn. When she went to get her books she dropped a hint about something she might do later. I didn't pick up at that moment. When she was gone i realized what she was saying. I called her immediately to tell her not to do it. She didn't answer. I was kinda scared that night thinking about it. I was scared as i thought that if i saw something the next day i wouldn't forgive myself. I knew what she meant and i could have stoped it but i didn't. 

So now today.. I went to the bus stop and had to run back home to get my geometry project. I don't do well in the cold. My lungs practically stop working. By the time i got back to the bus stop i was about ready to pass out. Then i went on the bus and just sat there looking out the window. I thought i was going to puke. It really didn't help that the kid behind me kept breathing his nasty smelling breath into my seat. Then i got off the bus and was walking with Toni like i usually do. I got into school and went to my locker. I guess Leah saw me come in and came up to me with this devious look on her face. I figured out what it was about and i was like "NO!". I spent to much time on that project last night just to have her wreck it before i handed it in. Then i was telling her how i felt like i was going to puke so i sat next to the garbage can. She said she would help me get the lid off if i couldn't do it and puke at the same time. (Thanks!) Then i got a call from Stacy saying she was goin to meet me at my locker. Then Kristal came around and scared the crap out of me by slaming her crap on the desk i had my head on. Then i told her how crapy i felt and then she asked for some gum and i couldn't open it with out getting really sick feeling. So i told her to. She realized i wasn't joking so she just asked for my combination to my locker so she could put her stuff in there. Then we stayed until Stacy came. We just sat there for a little while as  i tried not to puke. Then lea's friend pilon's sister came over to me. I thought she was just going to say hi. I did spend one morning with her and i thought that we could be friends. I guess there is just something wrong with that family. She started telling me how lea said that she doesn't ever want to talk to me again, she doesn't want me to call her, she just wants me gone, and to stop talking about pilon n crap like that. So, i knew that lea probably wouldn't send someone over to me to tell me BS like that she would do it herself. I asked her if lea said this or if her sister said this. She sed "o no lea said all this". Then Stacy was all like i dont want to get involved. So i told her to go to her locker. Kristal, however, didnt want to go to Stacy's locker yet. So i told Kristal to come with me if she wanted to. As we left i saw that girl run by and tell lea something. Then i asked her what she told her to tell me and she's like "wat?". So i knew that flammer told her sister to say all that stuff. I was ready to kill her. i would have but i didn't want to get thrown out of school. All lea did was say no ur not going to touch her. The only thing that went through my head was that fine i'll get through u first. It won't be hard. Then i left because i knew i would definately do something i would regret. Then i went to Stacy's locker. Then went to drivers ed stayed for about ten minutes. Then asked to go to my locker and left. I was going to my locker and i saw lea and Javier. I dont know why i stayed with her. I cant remember if she was talking to me or whatever. But i stayed with her and Roni all first period. Then walked with her to math n stayed there but i didnt want the sub to mark me absent so i left there n went to bio. Then in Dr.'s class i asked to go to the bathroom and went for a walk with Roni. Then we picked up her friend. Then i sat in math almost dieing from sickness. then went to ROTC and almost died again. I remember the best part of my day. LUNCH!!! JACK WAS BACK IN SCHOOL!!!! then went to english and started to feel a little better. We had to do the WOD crap things again. In history i fell asleep. Made me feel so much better! I was walking with Kristal and she asked if her face was red and i said a little. then i asked her and she said no. Then we meet up with Stacy and she was like "HOLY CRAP WHAT HAPPENED TO YOUR FACE! WERE U SLEEPING OR SOMETHING!" i just looked at Kristal and laughed. Then i went to spanish and then left to go on a walk. Yes, that was a twenty minute walk!! I'm proud. it was fun. i was by myself for a while then i found Ryan and we talked for like 2 mins then me n Leah walked the rest of the school. Then we went back to spanish and taped my desk so it wouldn't be able to flip open like it usually does. Then the bell rang. The best part of the day. 

I'm just going to go on about things i don't get. Things i hate. And things i do when im alone.
I dont get people, i dont get how u can care so much for someone who treats you like your worthless, i dont get proofs!!, i dont get why all of a sudden Stacy keeps things from me, i dont get why i do the things i do, I dont get why i get so depressed when im alone, i dont get why i go into depression mood whenever there isn't a friend by my side, i dont get why things happen, i dont get why life sucks, i dont get how people say high school is suposed to be the time of your life when it really hurts you worse than anything in the world, i dont get how i can have a crush so soon when i think im fallin out of love, i dont get why i always have to get hurt, i dont get why i think about all the saddest things, i dont get why i cry so much over one person i might not have even met, i dont know why i didnt do all honors classes freshman year like i should have, i dont like thinking about wat if i went to Mon Don like my mom wanted me to, i don't get why people kill themselves when there are people who have no choice about living.. i guess thats all for now. Im bored with this.

ok ryan this is for u... since u sed i needed 2 update i will.. only cuz i love u...
sooo... where do i start...i'll start with good times. then i'll move onto the bad times.. like 2day n the day b4... book hot gay sex came up... that is one funny book.. it says things like with this coupon i will spank u jus until the red appears.. lol..then marilyn decided 2 "get" it.. ok.. the good times are over...then school came around again.. i think all this crap started on wednesday or mayb tuesday.. i dont remember but  stacy n kelsey were gettin into a fight.. then one day kelsey was gunna pay sum1 to beat her up.. i thought that sounded kinda strange... so all through rotc she was screaming n yelling about it.. i was ready 2 hit her.. thats like almost 2 hrs straight she went through.. geeeze.. n then i asked kelsey about it cuz i wanted 2 no who she was gunna get 2 do this so i could tell stacy to watch out 4 this person.. n kelsey sed wat r  u talking about.. n then wrote her  a note.. n i got in trouble... then 2day she flips out on me n says u have a big effin mouth n cant keep a secret.. so that was it i was so pissed.. i needed 2 vent or i'd hurt her or sum1... i couldnt say nething in lunch b/c stacy has 2 sit by marilyn who is like the only 1 who actually knows wat stacy is like.. so i was like i'll tell u sum other time.. n then iwas gunna talk 2 tanya cuz she was jus sayin that she knew how stacy was sometimes.  but of course stacy had 2 be standing there 2.. so i jus droped it until english .. i got my mind off it by teaching poppe how 2 do her algebra..then i helped kristen with hers cuz i found her error..then  i went to english  n i talked 2 kelsey n stephanie about it.. thank god 4 kelsey then..that girl jus pisses me off sometimes.. n she knows she does it 2.. n then like the next time i see her she acts like nothing happened.. well wen scott leaves she'll know how much she needs me.. who would do her homework? who will she hang out with? who
